        <item>
            <title>林超英：開冷氣會通知大家　出梗圖「唔好再問我有無開冷氣」</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/08/06/lamchiuying-report-safety-on-facebook/life-tech/green-2/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=lamchiuying-report-safety-on-facebook</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/08/06/lamchiuying-report-safety-on-facebook/life-tech/green-2/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Ngan Ivan]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Tue, 06 Aug 2024 08:00:47 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[健康]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[城中熱話]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[環保]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Luna Is A Bep]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[冷氣]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[林超英]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1254881</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p style="font-weight: 400;">前天文台台長林超英向來提倡環保，甚少開冷氣的他長期在電費單上維持負七元。最近他就在自己的 Facebook 專頁上向大家報平安表示自己沒有熱倒，感激廣大市民在炎熱天氣下仍然關心他有沒有開冷氣。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1254885 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/123135429-562x580.jpg" alt="林超英" width="562" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/123135429-562x580.jpg 562w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/123135429.jpg 872w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 562px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">圖片來源：<a href="https://www.facebook.com/lamchiuyinghk/posts/pfbid02e1pRuQjXkHs3ob1XNkNSNniqStje2YBzMmyRvuuFYifJciDYCzoxonigZpQWqXrVl?rdid=DHonRtnNabSLyD9w">Facebook @林超英 Lam Chiu Ying</a></p><p style="font-weight: 400;">天文台在昨日錄得全年最高溫記錄的 35.4 度，林超英在 Facebook 上表示自己依舊沒有開冷氣。林超英在貼文中附上了自己的工作桌照片，桌上擺放了手提電腦和不同的文件，還擺放了一把小風扇。他表示自己都是在這樣的工作環境，靠着一把小風扇渡過一天的工作。他強調自己實在太熱也是會開冷氣的，而且開冷氣時會向大家交代，呼籲網民毋須天天詢問他有否開冷氣。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1254886 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/12-2-508x580.jpg" alt="" width="508" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/12-2-508x580.jpg 508w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/12-2.jpg 789w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 508px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">圖片來源：<a href="https://www.facebook.com/lamchiuyinghk/posts/pfbid02e1pRuQjXkHs3ob1XNkNSNniqStje2YBzMmyRvuuFYifJciDYCzoxonigZpQWqXrVl?rdid=DHonRtnNabSLyD9w">Facebook @林超英 Lam Chiu Ying</a></p><p style="font-weight: 400;">林超英的貼文引來了不少的網民讚好，欣賞他為了環保而身體力行，更佩服他的堅持。林超英亦在留言區上分享了與説唱歌手 Luna Is A Bep 合作推出宣揚環保訊息的歌曲《超英歌》 MV 截圖「唔好再問我有無開冷氣」，重申如果有開冷氣會通知大家。</p><p style="font-weight: 400;">資料來源：<a href="https://www.facebook.com/lamchiuyinghk/posts/pfbid02e1pRuQjXkHs3ob1XNkNSNniqStje2YBzMmyRvuuFYifJciDYCzoxonigZpQWqXrVl?rdid=DHonRtnNabSLyD9w">Facebook @林超英 Lam Chiu Ying</a></p><p style="font-weight: 400;">圖片來源：<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=NAf72Bwg3uA">Hong Kong 2050 is NOW</a></p><br /><b>相關文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/08/06/adac-test-reveals-the-effects-of-aircon-on-ev-range/life-tech/auto/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">德國最大汽車協會科學測試，空氣調節對電動車續航力影響</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/08/06/lamchiuying-report-safety-on-facebook/life-tech/green-2/">林超英：開冷氣會通知大家　出梗圖「唔好再問我有無開冷氣」</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
            <wfw:commentRss>https://unwire.hk/2024/08/06/lamchiuying-report-safety-on-facebook/life-tech/green-2/feed/</wfw:commentRss>
